    areaTitle: 'We Serve the Charlotte Metro and Carolinas', areaSub: 'Based in Fort Mill, SC, we clean air ducts for homes across York County and the south Charlotte area. Pick your city below for local details.', areaInfoHeading: 'Cleaner Air Across the Region', areaInfoBlurb: 'We bring NADCA-standard equipment to homes throughout York County and south Charlotte. Locally owned, licensed, and insured.',
